    <narrativeNotes>Grignr, thunder-god, was one of the many shards of Grignr shattered through time, but was one of the small few that fell into the Backrooms. This Grignr abandoned his rage and barbarian ways instead seeking the harmony and peace that came with ancient Chinese practices, become a powerful cultivator of Chi energy. During his time in the backrooms, he dedicated unknowable time to continuing his meditation, until eventually he was called upon to the fight the experimental Mjolnir mechanoid, which threatened his new home. After defeating this seemingly invincible foe Grignr was crowned Grignr Thunder-God by his wife, Angra, and their companions.</narrativeNotes>
